sp.p:
He was opposed to our marriage, and though in compliance with the king’s commands he gave
       his consent to our union; yet from that moment we were forbidden to approach his presence;
       whilst my once ample fortunes were ruined by the Restoration.

I must get this old fellow away as soon as possible;

 I'm sure he is not wanted here. And is it possible that you have given yourself
       the trouble of coming here, sir, merely for that.
